00039 void ProbeSetMultiDataDataTest::test_ChromosomeFromString()
00040 {

00042         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( ChromosomeFromString("Y") == Y_CHR);
00043         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( ChromosomeFromString("MT") == MT_CHR);
00044         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( ChromosomeFromString("--") == NO_CHR);
